---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy | DoneOps" description="DoneOps Privacy Policy — how we collect, use, and protect your information.">
  <Header slot="header" isSubPage={true} />

  <article class="py-12 lg:py-20 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <Breadcrumbs crumbs={[
          { name: "Home", url: "/" },
          { name: "Privacy Policy", url: "/privacy-policy/" },
        ]} />

        <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mb-12">Last updated: April 2, 2026</p>

        <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none
          prose-headings:text-slate-900 dark:prose-headings:text-slate-100
          prose-p:text-slate-700 dark:prose-p:text-slate-300
          prose-a:text-primary-600 dark:prose-a:text-primary-400
          prose-li:text-slate-700 dark:prose-li:text-slate-300">

          <p>DoneOps ("we," "our," or "us") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard information when you visit our website at <a href="https://doneops.com">doneops.com</a>.</p>

          <h2>Information We Collect</h2>

          <h3>Information You Provide</h3>
          <p>When you use our contact form, we collect:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Your name</li>
            <li>Your email address</li>
            <li>Your message content</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Contact form submissions are processed through <a href="https://www.netlify.com/privacy/">Netlify Forms</a> and delivered to our team via email.</p>

          <h3>Information Collected Automatically</h3>
          <p>When you visit our website, we may automatically collect:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Usage data</strong> through Google Analytics (GA4), including pages visited, time spent on pages, referral sources, and general geographic region. Google Analytics uses cookies to collect this data. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy">Google's Privacy Policy</a> for details.</li>
            <li><strong>Bot detection data</strong> through Google reCAPTCHA v3, which helps protect our contact form from spam. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy">Google's Privacy Policy</a> for details on reCAPTCHA data processing.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Respond to your inquiries submitted through our contact form</li>
            <li>Understand how visitors use our website so we can improve it</li>
            <li>Protect our website from spam and abuse</li>
          </ul>
          <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>

          <h2>Cookies</h2>
          <p>Our website uses the following cookies and similar technologies:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Google Analytics cookies</strong> — to collect pseudonymous usage statistics</li>
            <li><strong>Google reCAPTCHA cookies</strong> — to protect our contact form from automated submissions</li>
            <li><strong>Theme preference</strong> — a localStorage entry to remember your dark/light mode preference (not a cookie, no data leaves your browser)</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p>Our website uses the following third-party services:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Netlify</strong> — website hosting and form processing</li>
            <li><strong>Google Analytics (GA4)</strong> — website analytics</li>
            <li><strong>Google reCAPTCHA v3</strong> — spam protection</li>
            <li><strong>Google Fonts</strong> — web typography</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Data Retention</h2>
          <p>Contact form submissions are retained for as long as necessary to respond to your inquiry and maintain our business records. Analytics data is retained according to Google Analytics' default retention settings.</p>

          <h2>Your Rights</h2>
          <p>You have the right to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Request access to the personal information we hold about you</li>
            <li>Request correction or deletion of your personal information</li>
            <li>Opt out of analytics tracking by using browser privacy settings or extensions</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>Our website is not directed at children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>

          <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>

          <h2>Contact Us</h2>
          <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your data, please contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@doneops.com">hello@doneops.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</BaseLayout>
